<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
<small class="text-muted">Effective Date: 10/29/2025</small>

<p>This Privacy Policy explains how the site ("we", "our", or "us") collects, uses, and protects information from users ("you") who access or use our site and game.
    This site was developed as an academic project and is not intended for commercial use.
</p>
<h3>Information We Collect</h3>
<p>
    We collect only the minimum information required by users to create and use an account, such as:
    <ul>
        <li>Username (chosen by user)</li>
        <li>Password (securely stored in hashed form)</li>
        <li>Name</li>
        <li>Email</li>
        <li>Age</li>
        <li>Generalized location (by US State)</li>
    </ul>
    We do <strong>not</strong> collect, request, or store any forms of payment information.
</p>
<h3>How We Use Information</h3>
<p>
    We use the collected information solely to:
    <ul>
        <li>Authenticate users so they can sign in and play the game</li>
        <li>Maintain basic account functionality</li>
    </ul>
    No data is used for advertising, analytics, or shared with any external services.
</p>
<h3>Information Sharing</h3>
<p>
    We do <strong>not</strong> share, sell, or transfer any user information to third parties.
    User data remains within the app's internal database and is accessible only to authorized developers maintaining the project.
</p>
<h3>Data Security</h3>
<p>
    Passwords are stored using industry-standard hashing practices.
    While reasonable security measures are in place, this project is for educational use only and is not designed for production-level data protection.
</p>
<h3>Cookies and Tracking</h3>
<p>
    This site may use basic session cookies to keep users logged in.
    These cookies do not track browsing activity and contain no personal data.
</p>
<h3>Children's Privacy</h3>
<p>
    This app is intended for general audiences and does not knowingly collect information from children under 13 years of age. Individuals under the age of 13 are
    prohibited from registering for an account. Parental discretion and supervision required for individuals under 13 years of age.
</p>
<h3>Contact</h3>
<p>
    If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, you may contact the developer at: <a href="mailto:COvermyer@my.gcu.edu">COvermyer@my.gcu.edu</a>
</p>
<h3>Updates to This Policy</h3>
<p>
    This Privacy Policy may be updated if the project changes or adds new features. The latest version of this policy will always be available on this page.
</p>